xt-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">RE: Wendell Charles Nesmith<span style="white-space: pre;">	</span>DOB: 27/06/1984</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">Dear Wendell,</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">As you are aware you are on Psychiatric Treatment Order which requires to follow treatment advice/reccomentations to better your mental well-being and quality of life. I am happy to discuss treatment options with you achieve your goals. To facilitate this we need your utmost co-operation. This includes following the treatment advice that we agree on. I wish to monitor metabolic risk factors and serum levels of Olanzapine, to assist gradual transition from depot Olanzapine to oral Olanzapine. I also request you not to do any video recording without seeking permission from the person you are recording.</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">I hope get favourable response from you to this letter. I am looking forward to having collaborative discussions regarding your treatments and clinical needs.</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">thanking you, Regards,</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">Dr<span style="white-space: pre;">	</span>urali Reddy Consultant Psychiatrist</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: c