sumer End of Care/ Discharge Summary<span style="white-space: pre;">	</span>11 May 2016</p><p style="text-align: center;">("Cairns Discharge Summary")</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">QLD Government, Progress Notes, Outpatient,<span style="white-space: pre;">	</span>9 June 2016 and</p><p style="text-align: center;">8. ("Cairns Outpatient Progress Notes")<span style="white-space: pre;">	</span>5 July 2016</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">QLD Government Mental Health Services (Atherton</p><p style="text-align: center;">9. MHS), Consumer Care Review Summary and Plan</p><p style="text-align: center;">("Cairns Care Review")</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">7 July 2016</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">o. DOCUMENTS FILED. BY APPELLANT ON APPEAL</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">1. Application for appeal<span style="white-space: pre;">	</span>7 September 2018</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">2. Application for leave to appeal out of time</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">14 September 2018</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">E. DOCUMENTS FILED BY RESPONDENT ON APPEAL</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">1. Submission in relation to Appellant's website<span style="white-space: pre;">	</span>2 November 2018</p><p