seen again hY our services until this year.</p><p style="text-align: center;">When asked about this hospital Incident r cently Mr Nesmith talked about being "embarrassed" It had happened and that It was "sexual. experimentation" that went horribly wrong, as he wanting to try and "Increase sexual stimulation".</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">In regards to other psychiatric presentations, Mr Nesmith has spoken about being "locked up" In hospitals in various places In NSW, at least on 2 occasions, With him believing he was being "censored" for his beliefs and part of a greater conspiracy and cover-up. He was reluctant to give details of his time In hospital or precise locations. He could 11st by name several antlpsychotlcs used (olanzapine, risperidone, quetlaplne) and the awful side effects experienced, adding to his negative experience. It does not seem he has ever taken an\lpsychotlcs long-term, only In restrictive environments.</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">Created By: Dr Caroline Flynn (Registrar) Printed By: Dr Caroline Fly_nn (Registrar)</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">Page 8 of 14</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">There Is no known history of his earlier years In the US before he moved to Australia. He states he Is estranged from his us parents and siblings because they 11don't believe In my cause". He Is adamant he does not want contact with them, We have not found any longer-term friend or contact for any collateral history alas.</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /